,["723"],"no-negated-in-lhs",["724"],"no-unused-vars","'Helmet' is defined but never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","JSXOpeningElement","no-dupe-keys","Duplicate key 'autoplay'.","ObjectExpression","unexpected","Duplicate key 'dots'.","jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/evcohen/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/master/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","'Link' is defined but never used.","'Component' is defined but never used.","'Slider' is defined but never used.","'modalIsOpen' is assigned a value but never used.","'setIsOpen' is assigned a value but never used.","'settings' is assigned a value but never used.","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation"]